Chọn khẳng định SAI trong các khẳng định sau

 

2.A

\[\mathop {\lim }\limits_{x \to + \infty } \left[ {{2^x}\left( {{x^2} + {x^4} + 1} \right)} \right] = + \infty \]

 

2.B

\[\mathop {\lim }\limits_{x \to + \infty } \frac{{\frac{3}{{{x^5}}} - \frac{1}{{{x^2}}} + {{\left( {\frac{1}{2}} \right)}^x}}}{3} = 0\]

 

2.C

\[\mathop {\lim }\limits_{x \to + \infty } \frac{{\left( {4 + \frac{1}{x} + \frac{1}{{{x^3}}}} \right)\left( {1 - \frac{1}{x}} \right)}}{{\left( {\frac{1}{x} - 1} \right)\left( {3 + \frac{1}{x}} \right)}} = \frac{4}{3}\]

 

2.D

\[\mathop {\lim }\limits_{x \to + \infty } \frac{{\frac{4}{x} + 1}}{{{x^3} + 1}} = 0\]

 

3.Đáp án

C

 

4.Đáp án chi tiết

\[\mathop {\lim }\limits_{x \to + \infty } \frac{{\left( {4 + \frac{1}{x} + \frac{1}{{{x^3}}}} \right)\left( {1 - \frac{1}{x}} \right)}}{{\left( {\frac{1}{x} - 1} \right)\left( {3 + \frac{1}{x}} \right)}} = \frac{4}{{\left( { - 1} \right).3}} = \frac{{ - 4}}{3}\]

 

5.Level

 

 

6.Ghi chú
